response.overview: Mufasa, a cub lost and alone, meets a sympathetic lion named Taka, the heir to a royal bloodline. The chance meeting sets in motion an expansive journey of a group of misfits searching for their destiny.
response.tagline: The story of an orphan who would be king.
response.title: Mufasa: The Lion King
